headline: U.S. Bank’s Elavon Jumps Two Spots in 2025 Nilson Report Ratings
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, April 09, 2025--Elavon, the merchant services payment provider of U.S. Bank, has moved up two spots in the 2025 Nilson Report to become the fifth-largest U.S. merchant acquirer and the second-largest bank-owned acquirer as ranked by Mastercard and Visa purchase volume.
